Name: market group for diesel | diesel | EN15804GD, U
Category: C:Manufacturing/19:Manufacture of coke and refined petroleum products/192:Manufacture of refined petroleum products/1920:Manufacture of refined petroleum products
Description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/14042/documentation

This dataset is a market group. Market groups represent a 'market of markets'. Their purpose is to group a set of markets into larger, geographically relevant datasets.;Market groups are created for convenience and ease of use. They only group other markets and/or market groups contained within their geography.;Losses and relevant exchanges (transport, transport infrastructure, etc.) are not included in this dataset. They are present in the contained markets.  ;This is the market group for 'diesel', in Europe.

This activity starts at the gate of markets that deliver 'diesel', in geographies contained within the geography of this dataset.

This activity ends with the supply of 'diesel',  to the consumers of this product within the geography of Europe.
